FULLY COOKED EGG PATTY: WHOLE EGGS, WHEY, SOYBEAN OIL, NONFAT MILK. CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SALT, XANTHAN GUM, CITRIC ACID, NATURAL BUTTER FLAVOR. PASTEURIZED PROCESS AMERICAN CHEESE: CHEDDAR CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES), WATER, SODIUM CITRATE, MILKFAT, SALT, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, SORBIC ACID (PRESERVATIVE), APO-CAROTENAL (COLOR), SOY LECITHIN (NON-STICKING AGENT).
